          "id": "s:83a1a6c6e80240ddf1a5c8d40f94dd27590c246e",
          "name": "Shāh Ashraf Hotak, (Pashto, Dari: ), also known as Shāh Ashraf Ghiljī (Pashto: شاه اشرف غلجي‎ ) (died 1730), son of Abdul Aziz Hotak, was the fourth ruler of the Hotak dynasty.",
