          "name": " He is best known for writing and directing \"Road Trip\" (2000), \"Old School\" (2003), \"Starsky & Hutch\" (2004), \"The Hangover Trilogy\" (2009, 2011, and 2013), \"Due Date\" (2010) and \"War Dogs\" (2016).",
