          "id": "s:efe5d05aa2c16e565c1b2a55305df99eb1a2204a",
          "name": " The attack into the Lombardy Plain by the 15th Allied Army Group started on 6 April 1945, ending on 2 May with the formal surrender of German forces in Italy.",
